{"tid":2491474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"性感撩髮+美背全裸太犯規！TWICE SANA推第一本個人寫真書　火辣背殺照讓粉絲全暴動","createTime":"2021-04-16T10:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T10:44:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"835753c15e2f576a48350d1c47bb57212ce34c9b","tid":2491474,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T10:44:40.000Z","msg":"TWICE成員個個擁有絕美外貌與纖細體態，自出道以來受到許多粉絲歡迎，每每推出新歌都能引起一陣話題。近年，TWICE成員紛紛推出個人寫真書，由「忙內」（子瑜）打頭陣，在去年三月率先推出男友視角滿滿的《Yes, I am Tzuyu.》，接著在12月由日籍成員Mina接棒，推出同名寫真書《Yes, I am Mina.》。跟子瑜的鄰家女孩風不同，Mina的寫真風格給人更加成熟冷艷的感覺，與他貴族千金小姐的氣質非常相配。接著，推出個人寫真書的第三位成員同樣是來自日本的SANA（湊崎紗夏），以度假作為主題，邀請ONCE（粉絲名）一同展開暫時逃離都市的小小療癒之旅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/16/1/12102847.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2F1%2F12102847.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=c4d396ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSANA的寫真書非常有他個人的風格，除了有性感風格之外，也有不少居家、男友視角的美照。在三月釋出的預告短片中，SANA先是展現了在田野間的休閒模樣，穿著連身洋裝、紮起低馬尾，非常有文藝氣息。接著畫面帶到海邊，戴著貝蕾帽、穿著格紋襯衫的他悠閒散步，不時對著鏡頭甜笑給人滿滿的女友感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/16/1/12102816.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2F1%2F12102816.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=e6874803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/16/1/12102819.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2F1%2F12102819.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=47be4fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/16/1/12102818.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2F1%2F12102818.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=ca36b25b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過最後他換上黑色削肩開衩禮服，在海邊展現了極致性感，尤其背部全裸的回眸照更是讓不少粉絲瞬間感到心動不已，難得一見的性感服裝也讓粉絲都暴動了。另外一段預告短片也非常有看頭，SANA接連換上黑色芭蕾服、Oversize襯衫、白色深V開襟上衣、碎花洋裝、淺藍色深V洋裝在室內空間拍攝，每一套造型都非常值得珍藏。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/16/1/12102866.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2F1%2F12102866.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=d4497c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/16/1/12102848.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2F1%2F12102848.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=65ea9117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/04/16/1/12102849.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F04%2F16%2F1%2F12102849.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D750&h=e8626cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://